所有程序包的分层结构

程序包分层结构:
  • org.zollty.log,
  • org.zollty.log.jul14,
  • org.zollty.log.log4j

类分层结构

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.log4j.AppenderSkeleton (implements org.apache.log4j.Appender, org.apache.log4j.spi.OptionHandler)
      • org.apache.log4j.WriterAppender
        • org.apache.log4j.FileAppender
          • org.zollty.log.log4j.DailyRollingFileAppender
    • org.zollty.log.ConsoleAppender (implements org.zollty.log.Logger, org.zollty.log.LoggerSupport, java.io.Serializable)
      • org.zollty.log.ConsoleLogger
    • java.util.logging.Handler
      • org.zollty.log.jul14.SLF4JBridgeHandler
    • org.zollty.log.Jdk14Logger (implements org.zollty.log.Logger, org.zollty.log.LoggerSupport, java.io.Serializable)
      • org.zollty.log.ConsoleJdk14Logger
    • org.zollty.log.Level
    • org.zollty.log.Log4jLogger (implements org.zollty.log.Logger, org.zollty.log.LoggerSupport, java.io.Serializable)
    • org.zollty.log.LogFactory
    • org.zollty.log.LogFactory.LogManager
    • org.zollty.log.LoggerExeInfo
    • org.zollty.log.LoggerInfo (implements java.io.Serializable)
    • org.zollty.log.LoggerManager
    • org.zollty.log.LoggerManager.LoggerExeCountComparator (implements java.util.Comparator<T>, java.io.Serializable)
    • org.zollty.log.LoggerWrapper (implements org.zollty.log.Logger, org.zollty.log.LoggerWrapperAPI, java.io.Serializable)
    • org.zollty.log.LogUtils
